Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:42.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the representative for the Derrink Company,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:44.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lutz Eringin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:46.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Craft Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:59.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H575F66&\4c&H575F66&\pos(640,504)\blur3\1c&HCCD4DD&}Wolf and Lonely Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you are from the Rowen trading guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:05.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:11.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been treated quite favorably due to the efforts of the Lord Goldens of your guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:15.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At my level I only know the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:20.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy, you look quite splendid yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:25.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And your companion also has a true air of nobility about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:31.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I would like to announce the decision we came to after our discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:34.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,2000 Trenni silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:39.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Boland representative suggested a price of 2500 Trenni silver,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:43.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but as I understand the purpose of this is the fur trading, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:48.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That much may be excessive for individual trading.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:51.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To compensate, we won't charge a handling fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pay the full 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:57.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as we don't have such a quantity of Trenni silver on hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:03:02.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,payment will be 60 Lumione gold coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:08.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How generous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:12.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a crafty person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:18.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've prepared a means by which to gain profit from the state of this city and its social condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:21.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect this will be your gateway to prominence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We merely wish to share in your luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:27.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:31.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing but good fortune that led you two to meet in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:35.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, you remain calm in the face of such a large deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:39.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I take this to mean you are accustomed to good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:43.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In our line of work, luck is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:46.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Without it you'd lose your footing in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:50.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on that, we'll place our trust in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:51.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:54.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How will the funds be transferred?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:57.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be buying furs from the Arkie Company, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really have a good eye for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:03.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do teach me your methods sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:05.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My voice is hoarse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking is unpleasant. {zing}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:19.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:30.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to sleep with a sparkling pile of gold coins by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:41.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When dealing with large amounts of money, people tend to get conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:46.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They become demanding and put on a false composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, it's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:52.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You manage to word it so as to sound modest, but you remain sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:04.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So will it be satisfactory to receive the cash just before your purchase?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:14.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us pray our dealings go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What an unpleasant man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:28.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I've dealt with a person like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It made me realize just how small of a merchant I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:41.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As someone who fusses over a couple hundred silver coins, I feel he's in a different league.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:45.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you had some pretty sharp replies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:49.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's new for me to hear comebacks like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:51.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eringin was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:54.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like "I can't take town merchants lightly."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:59.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not some noble son from a huge company?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are nights I think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:04.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:06.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:09.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,where did you meet your companion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the question such a surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:15.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I wouldn't pry, but it does interest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I get asked a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:25.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be shocked if you told me she was the daughter of fallen nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:27.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was apparently born in the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:32.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was living in a village that grows wheat south of here for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was visiting that village on business one time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,she snuck herself onto my cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:43.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wanted to return to the north, so although it's had complications,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:45.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been guiding her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:49.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like the kind of meeting a cheap poet would write about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:50.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though those 'complications' sound interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:57.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they're the type you couldn't even confess to a priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't discuss them {\i1}because{\i0} it's a priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you have her wearing quality clothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I expect it was a good meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:08.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd kept quiet, she'd have just bought them herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She does have a smart appearance to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:14.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I expect she's nice under those clothes too.{Norg: er} { FOTC: She's talking about the relationship. What the hell are you thinking, Norg? Can't wrap your brain around the fact that women are not just holes for Big Jim and the Twins? } {wtf big jim? is there anything you americans don't have a name for?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:17.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I suggest you keep it down when you're in the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:24.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can buy meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can't choose their quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:29.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure your meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:35.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who bought me was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:41.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In my country, the wool trade is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:47.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was into buying futures and poured in huge amounts of money,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:50.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the King changed policies and he went bankrupt in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:54.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, because he had more pride than a noble,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,on the day his bankruptcy was decided,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:59.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,he cut his own throat with a knife and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:03.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least it was a manly ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The wedding ceremony was really gaudy as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:14.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps was crying on about how it would be one of the best in Boland family history.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:17.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, to me it was more like a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, there were some benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One was that I no longer had to worry about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:26.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The other was I didn't have to bear children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:32.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And also that nobody found out about the money I was slipping from his purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The house and all the assets were taken when he went bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was plenty of money left to start a business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:46.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to surpass his company's success.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:49.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To show that he was just lucky to be able to buy me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:55.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm not so cheap that someone like him could buy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:59.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so childish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:00.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I just want someone to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was jealous of you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, please forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:22.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We should only be concerned with making a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:32.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the outcome of the meeting has been publicly announced, we'll move right into negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:35.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to keep the old man informed of where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:36.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal should go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was seriously an annoying waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were as meek as a kitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:54.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing I could do but sit quietly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:57.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you really helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to ask whether those ramblings were true or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:09.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand why you made all the decisions yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:15.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you rely on me a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:19.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're feeling the weight of selling me off, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:25.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:29.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you practice at anything, you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try practicing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:32.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Relying on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd fall for that so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:45.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really have gotten used to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:50.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But your soft-heartedness will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:53.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be so reserved after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:55.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, for a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:57.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:03.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:11.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People change with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:15.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little while ago, if I were doing this, you'd freeze up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch it so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:30.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going to start panicking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say what it is you're thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:35.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I might start panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:37.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:40.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to start panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:42.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.{キッス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:55.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's end our journey here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:12.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:17.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a contract with you to bring you to your hometown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:22.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already come pretty close, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:26.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:27.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:30.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That fox said so, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Treasure your meeting."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:35.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So profound for a human female.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:40.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to treasure our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:44.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why parting here is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to treasure our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way I can accept that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:52.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This journey has truly been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Laughing, crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:13:00.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with me being as cunning as I am, yelling like a kid when we fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:05.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a stunning experience for my body after being alone for such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:13.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly want this to continue forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:19.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I'm scared of the thought that I'll be at your deathbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already used to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:27.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're such a soft-hearted person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:31.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do, you accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:42.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:44.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm afraid of is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bantering with you is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:01.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So much that I want to eat you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:05.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you only eat tasty things, what'll happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:07.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's better tomorrow than it was today,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:12.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and better the day after than it is tomorrow, you'll expect it to become even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:16.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But what lies at the end of those ever-rising steps?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:19.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Before long, we won't be able to be satisfied,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,our fun banter will become weather-worn,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and all that'll be left is faded memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:30.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared of having our fun times sped up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,because of your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:43.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you seen even one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:46.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A tale that continues happily ever after?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the verge of realizing your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:56.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no more suitable time than now to end the tale, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps. {WRONG ANSWER!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish reading it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:16.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's mostly the same as what I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:21.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go return it before I spill wine on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:24.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:29.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You might also fall asleep reading and drool all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't snore either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:38.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to hear what you say in your sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please, don't eat any more than this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:45.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm properly earning my eating expenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just saying that in retrospect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we hadn't made a profit in Kumerson,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:54.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I would literally have been eaten out of house and home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They say when you've tasted the poison, you might as well finish the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:02.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, I'll eat you up as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:02.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:06.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to eat after we go return the books?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave that till later to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens, please let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:21.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to Rigolo's place for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:28.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That inn's going to become your shop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:29.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be happier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a joyous occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:42.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like some people are unhappy with the decision they came to in the Fifty-man meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:46.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more accurate to say they're already making arrangements in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:49.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you and that fox partnered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's merely a temporary agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:17:00.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like that sleazy store owner is keeping an eye on her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:03.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can just get the money, I'm sure it'll all go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's going favorably. {KNOCK ON FUCKING WOOD}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's almost scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:14.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Only because you've run into so many problems before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's worth 2000 silver, you know. {/a/ be all over this shit}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:31.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you bought wine with all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:34.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be able to buy an unbelievable amount of choice goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it goes well, I'll give you as much as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:39.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:43.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drink enough to puke before I get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you drank yourself into that state,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd keep drinking without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:48.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:58.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rigolo is out, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:03.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something you want to read?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:06.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please feel free to take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:11.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're valuable, books are books.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:15.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better that someone read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:18.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure not to be careless with the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:32.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always strange seeing green and white leaves in the middle of winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:34.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:38.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rigolo said that if you put effort into it you can maintain it like this all year, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:41.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that too arrogant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:52.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:20.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:23.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The holy mother's face is made so well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:25.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd pour out my worries to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:26.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:29.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Rigolo in a meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they called him out all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:34.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't supposed to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll pretend I didn't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for prying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:45.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to hear about this glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:52.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This glass was patiently constructed piece by piece over the course of three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:53.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Over three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:59.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when called for work, he'd gaze at his garden till the brink of the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:02.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he'd rather be doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:05.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,scribing is an important job isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:09.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,God also says that work is a precious thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:10.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:17.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,his carefree wish to live in his garden watching over it every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,might just be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:22.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I catch myself thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:26.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Humble dreams are the hardest to make true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:28.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And those times...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:34.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The times I thought that I'd like to watch him forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,might be the times I find most fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:52.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your words touched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:53.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:04.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that being able to follow a humble dream forever is truly a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Find any good books?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:13.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:17.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I had bit of an enlightening talk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:22.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What might that be? {holy shit woman do you always knock like that?} { FOTC: You don't want to be the door? Weirdo. }
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:33.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:36.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Lawrence in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:39.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Abe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving!
